{"tid":489050,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸自辦駕駛執照初體驗分享","createTime":"2017-12-04T10:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T05:32:37.000Z","uid":150857,"like":7,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"08eb6b083578ba72b3e9e4600585d110c388f292","tid":489050,"uid":150857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:04:12.000Z","msg":"大陸辦駕照要有3寶<br />\n1.居住証<br />\n2.體檢報告<br />\n3.正式駕駛執照(當然包括hkid同歡樂卡)<br />\n<br />\n個人經歷如下<br />\n今日上午9:00到派出所辦理居住証，要有住房租賃合同or房產証，以及個人照片連回執(回執係照片通過審核的便條)半小時內辦完<br />\n之後打的去西麗車管所(點解去西麗？因為果度有體檢及辦駕照一條龍，唔洗再煩)<br />\n到左果度再即使網上預算，2分鐘後取號，大約等5分鐘就叫你，之後比晒d資料佢就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw車管所人員好有禮貌，完全出乎我意料，全程幫我，包括預約同埋取號，讚👍"},{"pid":"cbf54244c939e76957b15e2cb01a75bd2cac9a11","tid":489050,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:05:43.000Z","msg":"你點整到居住證？"},{"pid":"a2567c7518b256025eb868ea697d7456a689ece3","tid":489050,"uid":150857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:07:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你點整到居住證？</blockquote><br />\n暫住証sor"},{"pid":"f8a55fb3f6bbed179f540a5d233faf9ae5dc440b","tid":489050,"uid":62020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你點整到居住證？</blockquote><br />\n暫住証sor</blockquote><br />\n邊度整？<br />\n有無呢個既流程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2e55f88afc9873ecc26801454d492ca93c7642d","tid":489050,"uid":714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:11:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你點整到居住證？</blockquote><br />\n暫住証sor</blockquote><br />\n要點搞 我大陸無物業<br />\n同埋由申請到攞牌要幾耐"},{"pid":"5e6b48016a9345ba243482cd3816de25390d0155","tid":489050,"uid":714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:19:49.000Z","msg":"介唔介意留個tg比我問野"},{"pid":"3a40662a2101dddab5587196d0979ef8fc6a5b34","tid":489050,"uid":24080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T10:37:04.000Z","msg":"文錦渡果邊啲細鋪仔有全包<br />\n<br />\n我整果陣 好似600人仔<br />\n而家好似千一"},{"pid":"5427008db8dbc98530e038f6a657d0f27c5ea319","tid":489050,"uid":150857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你點整到居住證？</blockquote><br />\n暫住証sor</blockquote><br />\n邊度整？<br />\n有無呢個既流程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我就係沙頭派出所搞，因為個地址係果區，唔洗預約，你去到派出所就同門口保安講辦暫住証就得"},{"pid":"427da2dc76d2da231dc1e8b09c7eba36bd35a141","tid":489050,"uid":150857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你點整到居住證？</blockquote><br />\n暫住証sor</blockquote><br />\n要點搞 我大陸無物業<br />\n同埋由申請到攞牌要幾耐</blockquote><br />\n你可以用親戚朋友的地址，但注意要跟返所在地，e.g.親戚物業係廣州，你只能在廣州派出所辦理，另外你的資料有更改的話，都要返去果邊改<br />\n2.你熟悉流程可以一日辦完手續，但牌就要1至2個工作天先出到"},{"pid":"26c899060f379dbc7d9f75c76118cc513f56be25","tid":489050,"uid":150857,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T11:46:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>介唔介意留個tg比我問野</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/ivanchan1223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fivanchan1223&d=92pX4Sr7uSLFo4sFRTCm326kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=98405b75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/ivanchan1223</a><br />\n我盡答，因為我都第一次搞，只係個人經驗分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e630478bbb3f75c17c1dd449f8b51a2b3e53dd19","tid":489050,"uid":15271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:07:21.000Z","msg":"比千一人仔代理包晒啦"},{"pid":"f0c65c4215840cb37b9fa6b0484d78dac8ae4ae3","tid":489050,"uid":13450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"我都係自己整 500蚊人仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d649858e7d88ad7fb33efb57c3105ab7a6bbe2","tid":489050,"uid":150857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T23:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係自己整 500蚊人仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fa45400e314b8fc62b96f96ce5736d1de1e453","tid":489050,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T00:07:06.000Z","msg":"好感動, 香港人果然都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9850a18f2a7ae65751190daebda4d026a063f716","tid":489050,"uid":150857,"like":9,"dislike":20,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T00:11:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好感動, 香港人果然都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我對人唔對黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我承認自己係中國人，但愛國唔一定愛黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s不喜勿插"},{"pid":"d30582e97d1f2645f87fb7153a5c2e43f86c60b4","tid":489050,"uid":7442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T00:34:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你點整到居住證？</blockquote><br />\n暫住証sor</blockquote><br />\n要點搞 我大陸無物業<br />\n同埋由申請到攞牌要幾耐</blockquote><br />\n你可以用親戚朋友的地址，但注意要跟返所在地，e.g.親戚物業係廣州，你只能在廣州派出所辦理，另外你的資料有更改的話，都要返去果邊改<br />\n2.你熟悉流程可以一日辦完手續，但牌就要1至2個工作天先出到</blockquote><br />\n個往證人係咪可以唔洗自己名？"},{"pid":"b0dd33589fd1995f13cc3173cc60c4ab2d5c7a7b","tid":489050,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:27:41.000Z","msg":"我第一整係鏗錩俾左2000蚊<br />\n繼牌如果自己整會唔會有資料俾鏗錩鎖住，我自己整唔到？"},{"pid":"0826073785a832fa728ec8030203bbc4d4ce5ce1","tid":489050,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:28:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好感動, 香港人果然都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我對人唔對黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我承認自己係中國人，但愛國唔一定愛黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s不喜勿插</blockquote><br />\n大陸揸車爽到爆"},{"pid":"6ddf692944d4e4c234c8ca327339213b590cffd7","tid":489050,"uid":94177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T01:40:35.000Z","msg":"想問相片個回執點拎 定係去到辦事處樓下影穩陣<br />\n兩日後出左車牌有冇得叫佢寄出唔親身拎？"},{"pid":"0dd4c94ccb7893ad12eaa7074ea155122d9919a6","tid":489050,"uid":150857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T04:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你點整到居住證？</blockquote><br />\n暫住証sor</blockquote><br />\n要點搞 我大陸無物業<br />\n同埋由申請到攞牌要幾耐</blockquote><br />\n你可以用親戚朋友的地址，但注意要跟返所在地，e.g.親戚物業係廣州，你只能在廣州派出所辦理，另外你的資料有更改的話，都要返去果邊改<br />\n2.你熟悉流程可以一日辦完手續，但牌就要1至2個工作天先出到</blockquote><br />\n個往證人係咪可以唔洗自己名？</blockquote><br />\n實名制，你話呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8b0c795b08d4875c39590542f4c1cb88fa1ec81","tid":489050,"uid":150857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T04:04:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我第一整係鏗錩俾左2000蚊<br />\n繼牌如果自己整會唔會有資料俾鏗錩鎖住，我自己整唔到？</blockquote><br />\n唔會，因為暫住証維期只有1年，你下次繼牌就話搬左屋就ok"},{"pid":"4d4590854a37140d6fdd366691a2aa2c8280ecd8","tid":489050,"uid":150857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T04:09:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問相片個回執點拎 定係去到辦事處樓下影穩陣<br />\n兩日後出左車牌有冇得叫佢寄出唔親身拎？</blockquote><br />\n1.自助照相機，係你比左錢之後，會有照片9張及一張回執比你，唔洗擔心。如果係坊間影樓，你要問清楚佢影駕駛執照有冇回執，同埋影完要等佢上傳埋去警察局網頁先好比錢<br />\n2.你辦完手續，個姐姐會比一張交費便條比你，你拎張便條就可以去ems度做郵寄手續，一般一星期收到，但只限寄國內地址。最後記得交480牌費(用微信交)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5252d072b8cfc823c81b4c603987f1876385c5","tid":489050,"uid":18241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T05:15:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好感動, 香港人果然都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我對人唔對黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我承認自己係中國人，但愛國唔一定愛黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s不喜勿插</blockquote><br />\n愛國已經夠on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b220a9efe8d8d5e6623093779dda8d05de031f","tid":489050,"uid":150857,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:15:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好感動, 香港人果然都係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我對人唔對黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我承認自己係中國人，但愛國唔一定愛黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\np.s不喜勿插</blockquote><br />\n愛國已經夠on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大家都係炎黃子孫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 何必為左一個黨傷感情"},{"pid":"4955b4e1028372d8378bfa3e07fe58bffd36a85b","tid":489050,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T06:25:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸辦駕照要有3寶<br />\n1.居住証<br />\n2.體檢報告<br />\n3.正式駕駛執照(當然包括hkid同歡樂卡)<br />\n<br />\n個人經歷如下<br />\n今日上午9:00到派出所辦理居住証，要有住房租賃合同or房產証，以及個人照片連回執(回執係照片通過審核的便條)半小時內辦完<br />\n之後打的去西麗車管所(點解去西麗？因為果度有體檢及辦駕照一條龍，唔洗再煩)<br />\n到左果度再即使網上預算，2分鐘後取號，大約等5分鐘就叫你，之後比晒d資料佢就ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw車管所人員好有禮貌，完全出乎我意料，全程幫我，包括預約同埋取號，讚👍</blockquote><br />\n總共整幾多錢"},{"pid":"0a62d699bc04223f3bae1987fa9faf6c28735c64","tid":489050,"uid":134